                            <comment id="14467909" author="roshandawrani" created="Thu, 22 Oct 2009 12:55:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This behavior seems to have been introduced by the revision 17769 (faster exceptions handling - less InvokerInvokationException).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Because CachedMethod now MissingMethodException instead of InvocationTargetException, it is again caught by PogoMetaClassSite, which re-invokes that method causing an extra invocation of missingMethod.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should MissingMethodException get special handling in the changes that revision 17769 introduced and change &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (InvocationTargetException e) {
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; e.getCause() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; RuntimeException ? (RuntimeException)e.getCause() : &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; InvokerInvocationException(e);
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (InvocationTargetException e) {
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; (e.getCause() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; RuntimeException &amp;amp;&amp;amp; !(e.getCause() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; MissingMethodException)) ? (RuntimeException)e.getCause() : &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; InvokerInvocationException(e);
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14467966" author="roshandawrani" created="Fri, 23 Oct 2009 10:09:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed - was required only in 1.7 branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
